A man who knows and guesses absolutely everything participates in the Field of Miracles. Super game and prize one-bedroom apartment in Moscow. The studio is hiding and Yakubovich is voicing:
- So, a question from the history of the Russian State.
Yakubovich looked at the card and adds:
- The answer consists of two questions. If you answer both, you will receive a bonus to the main prize. Aaautomobile!
The man agreed.
Yakubovich:
- In my opinion, the second question will be easier than the first! Which one should we start with?
Man:
- Well, let's start with the second one ....
Yakubovich:
- So, silence in the studio! The second question.
- And in what year did this happen? You have a minute!
